➜今日大雪要滋补，不到10分钟做这样一碗面，驱寒保暖身体好！
http://www.sohu.com/a/436730365_100001467	20830
<p class="ql-align-center">转眼间，大雪至，冬天真的来了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">寒风萧瑟，万物渐次冰封，天气以寒冷为主</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">正是进补的好时节，我们可以多吃一些温补的食物以抵御寒冷</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这时候，没有什么比热气腾腾的美食更能温暖人心了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今天教大家用10分钟做一晚酸爽开胃又暖身的酸菜肥牛面~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201207/b7b0b678cfae4df8a215fe3af584300e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">食材：肥牛卷、洋葱、金针菇、杭椒、娃娃菜、鲜面条、泡菜、嫩豆腐、生抽、盐；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201207/5dbb4f15013b40deb20fa675990bfa11.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">第一步：焯肥牛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">肥牛解冻后和姜片起下沸水焯熟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不喜欢姜的可以放点料酒哦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">焯2分钟左右捞出备用</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201207/b06d6ffd7ef04a95984c2494c6801b9f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">第二步：炒蔬菜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">锅内油热后放入洋葱爆香</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">放入几片泡菜翻炒2分钟后加点生抽和盐调味</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后翻炒均匀，加热水煮开</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201207/6b455eb954b149fa83ce3cc30aa1d6cb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">第三步：煮面</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">水开后放入鲜面煮3分钟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">记得多搅拌几下，避免面黏连哦~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">3分钟后撒一把杭椒圈</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">放入嫩豆腐、金针菇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后铺上肥牛卷</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201207/b0b70cebb7f94814a3db22e9bdc6181c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">满满一大锅的肥牛面就煮好啦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">肥牛鲜香、豆腐嫩滑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">泡菜和洋葱开胃提香</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201207/9c36f5cf423848a28856de4bfcbdc30f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">肥牛和金针菇吸饱了汤汁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">酸酸辣辣的味道能轻易把人的胃口瞬间打开</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201207/c8a13896cf494c7bb85ce0f4a11e99c3.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">夹起一筷子送入嘴里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">刺激味蕾又嫩滑无比</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">能满足人所有的味觉体验</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201207/9cca45ee52804a3f97fbe4bd22e5d357.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">酸甜开胃的泡菜汤</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">加上香嫩的肥牛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再搭配筋道的面条</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">热乎乎的一碗有汤有汁吃起来即暖胃又有幸福感</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201207/a3ddf6c03dca4e0e97be296464d15226.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来碗热乎乎的泡菜肥牛！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">酸爽开胃！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">好吃到汤汁都不剩～</p>